libdiskusage-perl (0v0.8.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Update SNMP to use nsExtendOutput2Table
  * Update SNMP max message size to 15000
  * Add -H option to append list of hosts to targets
  * Update cron job to support a list of hosts to append to gscmnt config

